&lt;h3 id=&#34;报错解决&#34;&gt;报错解决&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;报错 &lt;code&gt;syntax error, unexpected &#39;xxx&#39; (T_CONSTANT_ENCAPSED_STRING), expecting &#39;)&#39;&lt;/code&gt; 咋办？&lt;/p&gt;
